description:
&lt;p&gt;Trust Temps are looking for dynamic and enthusiastic experienced Emergency Department registered nurses to provide care for the 200,000 patients that attend each year in our Emergency Departments. This role will suit an experienced registered ED nurse with excellent clinical knowledge and skills who is looking for a new challenge.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We offer flexible shifts, excellent rates of pay &amp; weekly pay.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;You will work in with critically unwell patients, minor illnesses, patients experiencing mental health crisis, paediatric patients and patients experiencing neurological emergencies. Queen’s ED is also part of the London/Essex Trauma Network and often receives Trauma patients via London Air Ambulance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If shortlisted, you will be invited to attend the Trust for testing, interview and to have your I.D documentation taken and relevant forms completed.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Alison Moore&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Trust Temps Recruitment Advisor&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: alison.moore40@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 01708 435000 ext 2851&lt;/p&gt;
